{"tid":1375373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線請停止屌支援","createTime":"2019-07-28T04:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:27:45.000Z","uid":261205,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"001a085a1d4a2f7d0feb0bb4930725be999104a9","tid":1375373,"uid":261205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:54:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋晚開始，見到幾個post都係自稱前線嘅屌後面支援叫佢地撒，hijack左整個抗爭意志。</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我想話，如果你地係真前線，與其你地事後屌，不如事前你地傾清楚exit strategy。因為臨場冇嘢可以傾到。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">總之記住，運動到而家為止，市民仍然企喺我地呢面，輿論仲有得打，都係因為大家不搳蓆，不分化。<br />\n冇民意，我地咩都唔係。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c4844d7d87d781d8092941856af7001c4af327e9","tid":1375373,"uid":232921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:55:18.000Z","msg":"自稱"},{"pid":"362ad3e61aea95cfa9d23e246e9de9d08d291fa5","tid":1375373,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"割"},{"pid":"3617533402a764d9bf7b4b2b9f6ad88267eeee67","tid":1375373,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">槍口一致對外<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"8cdf3ab35c2e899266dc1f0bb53b2496b812ddf6","tid":1375373,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:07:08.000Z","msg":"講真，我唔敢衝，但是都講AL 幫大家做airdrop.每個人都在付出。互相了解處境，不割蓆"},{"pid":"951f23078600e044c8931a0f21d3be2c05b4b79d","tid":1375373,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"你個title 太負面我有理由懷疑你都係分化撚以下請唔好再推<br />\n<br />\n================================================<br />\n<br />\n分化post 警報 三毛開前線屌和理, 和理屌前線既post 唔該唔好推<br />\n例子:<br />\n前線 有少部分人 開始咩都屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375273/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375273/page/1</a><br />\n睇住佢正評數直線上升, 回覆先睇幾頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請推正經做實事有建設既post<br />\n[727賽後檢討] 不要說:「你班勇武撚/散水撚/和理非撚, 咪阻住我<br />\n試著說:「我的隊友是另外兩種職業,我能如何配合他?」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375257/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375257/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"8f45dd97db8bf7fcc87ed90ff52a2b9b48b6792b","tid":1375373,"uid":261205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"951f23078600e044c8931a0f21d3be2c05b4b79d","tid":1375373,"uid":42431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"你個title 太負面我有理由懷疑你都係分化撚以下請唔好再推<br />\n<br />\n================================================<br />\n<br />\n分化post 警報 三毛開前線屌和理, 和理屌前線既post 唔該唔好推<br />\n例子:<br />\n前線 有少部分人 開始咩都屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375273/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375273/page/1</a><br />\n睇住佢正評數直線上升, 回覆先睇幾頁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請推正經做實事有建設既post<br />\n[727賽後檢討] 不要說:「你班勇武撚/散水撚/和理非撚, 咪阻住我<br />\n試著說:「我的隊友是另外兩種職業,我能如何配合他?」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1375257/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1375257/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:27:45.000Z","msg":"停止屌何來負面？"}]}